Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,艾絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.66,0:22:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼妳會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我是覺得來這裡 就能見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:22:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,艾絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.00,0:23:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,妳還能教我如何戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.96,0:23:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,明明發生了那樣的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.20,0:23:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的很狡猾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.16,0:23:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,艾絲小姐 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.18,0:23:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,還想要變強
